trans-unit.source: List Search Services (Azure Search Management REST API)
trans-unit.target: List Search Services (Azure Search Management REST API)

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>List Services</languageKeyword> operation returns a list of all Search services in the subscription of a specific resource group.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Services</languageKeyword> operation returns a list of all Search services in the subscription of a specific resource group.

trans-unit.source: This operation returns service definitions, minus the admin <codeInline>api-keys</codeInline>.
trans-unit.target: This operation returns service definitions, minus the admin <codeInline>api-keys</codeInline>.

trans-unit.source: Use the <link xlink:href="21dfc36c-e979-4aa3-9f33-1ceaed809546" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">List Admin Keys (Azure Search API)</link> to retrieve the admin keys.
trans-unit.target: Use the <link xlink:href="21dfc36c-e979-4aa3-9f33-1ceaed809546" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">List Admin Keys (Azure Search API)</link> to retrieve the admin keys.
